## --- CHATSPOT PROJECT SPECIFIC ---
# Ignore local environment settings (protects secrets/local DB strings)
ChatSpot/appsettings.json
ChatSpot/appsettings.Development.json

## --- BUILD ARTIFACTS ---
# Ignore compiled code and temporary build files
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
*.msi
*.exe
*.dll
*.pdb
*.nupkg

## --- IDE SETTINGS ---
# JetBrains Rider / IntelliJ
.idea/
*.sln.iml

# Visual Studio
.vs/
*.user
